nodes.text: Dustcrepes, also called dustcrêpes were a Tatooinian food commonly served with nausage. Luke Skywalker was known to enjoy them.
This light crepe was made of a dry type of bread, consisting of wheat. It also had a filling of herbivore meat.

Dustcrepes appeared in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. They could be made by traders, a profession that specialized in the creation of various goods, including food. Traders took the place of chefs and artisans, after those professions were removed from the game during the New Game Enhancements of November 15, 2005.
